{
    "$schema":  "https://app.kilo.ai/config.json#/template-only",
    "version":  "1.0.0",
    "generatedAt":  "2026-06-21",
    "purpose":  "Manifesto declarativo separando paths template-only (usados APENAS no desenvolvimento do template XForge) de paths user-facing (parte do esqueleto operacional que o usuario final precisa).",
    "specification":  "DR-0180 Fase 0",
    "templateOnly":  {
                         "description":  "Paths que existem SOMENTE para o time que desenvolve o template XForge. Devem ser EXCLUIDOS quando o usuario clonar o repo para usar como ponto de partida no projeto dele.",
                         "paths":  [
                                       ".git",
                                       ".xforge/decisions/",
                                       ".xforge/audit/",
                                       ".xforge/sessions/",
                                       ".xforge/feedback/",
                                       ".xforge/learning/",
                                       ".xforge/backlog/",
                                       ".xforge/roadmap/",
                                       ".xforge/sprints/",
                                       ".xforge/quality-gates/",
                                       ".xforge/memory/learning.jsonl",
                                       ".xforge/memory/sessions/",
                                       ".xforge/memory/known-errors.md",
                                       ".xforge/memory/known-decisions.md",
                                       ".xforge/memory/known-issues.md",
                                       "docs/decisions/",
                                       "docs/manual/",
                                       "CHANGELOG.md",
                                       "CLAUDE.md",
                                       "STATUS.md",
                                       "ARCHITECTURE.md"
                                   ],
                         "patterns":  [
                                          "*.audit.log",
                                          "*.dev-session.*",
                                          "*.internal.*"
                                      ],
                         "rationale":  "Esses paths contem decisoes internas (DRs), audit trails, sessoes de desenvolvimento, backlog/roadmap/sprints do time, e documentacao que descreve o desenvolvimento do template - nao o uso dele. Vazaria ruido desnecessario para o usuario final."
                     },
    "userFacing":  {
                       "description":  "Paths que fazem parte do esqueleto operacional. O usuario que clonar o template PRECISA desses paths (e apenas desses) para comeÃ§ar a trabalhar.",
                       "paths":  [
                                     ".kilo/",
                                     ".xforge/scripts/purify.ps1",
                                     ".xforge/scripts/init-consumer.ps1",
                                     ".xforge/scripts/reset-memory.ps1",
                                     ".xforge/scripts/diff-consumer.ps1",
                                     ".xforge/scripts/lib/",
                                     ".xforge/scripts/tests/",
                                     ".xforge/memory/index.json",
                                     ".xforge/memory/project-preferences.md",
                                     ".xforge/memory/current-context.md",
                                     ".xforge/project-dna/PROJECT-DNA.md",
                                     ".xforge/knowledge/INDEX.json",
                                     ".xforge/decisions/DR-0180-*.md",
                                     ".xforge/decisions/DR-0001-*.md",
                                     ".xforge/decisions/DR-0002-*.md",
                                     ".xforge/decisions/DR-0003-*.md",
                                     ".xforge/decisions/DR-0004-*.md",
                                     ".xforge/decisions/DR-0005-*.md",
                                     ".xforge/decisions/DR-0006-*.md",
                                     "kilo.jsonc",
                                     "AGENTS.md",
                                     "README.md"
                                 ],
                       "rationale":  "Esses paths dao ao usuario o minimo necessario: skills/agents/commands operacionais, scripts de manutencao (purify/init/reset/diff), manifesto template-only, knowledge INDEX com applicabilityScope, decisoes canonicas que regem o template, e o esqueleto de configuracao (.kilo + kilo.jsonc + AGENTS.md + README).",
                       "note":  "O .kilo/ inteiro e user-facing (operacional, substitui vel). Apenas as DRs canonicas (0001-0006 + 0180) vao junto, o resto das DRs internas e template-only."
                   },
    "scripts":  {
                    "purify":  {
                                   "path":  ".xforge/scripts/purify.ps1",
                                   "purpose":  "Detecta stack do projeto ativo, reescreve project-preferences.md e PROJECT-DNA.md, dedupa learning.jsonl. Cria backup. Suporta -WhatIf e -ProjectRoot.",
                                   "phase":  "1"
                               },
                    "init-consumer":  {
                                          "path":  ".xforge/scripts/init-consumer.ps1",
                                          "purpose":  "xforge init --consumer. Copia apenas paths userFacing para target dir. Reescreve contexto com stack detectado do target. Cria .xforge/template-only.json no destino.",
                                          "phase":  "0"
                                      },
                    "reset-memory":  {
                                         "path":  ".xforge/scripts/reset-memory.ps1",
                                         "purpose":  "xforge reset memory. Aplica manifest em projeto ja clonado: remove template-only paths, purifica memory, cria backup. Suporta -WhatIf.",
                                         "phase":  "0"
                                     },
                    "diff-consumer":  {
                                          "path":  ".xforge/scripts/diff-consumer.ps1",
                                          "purpose":  "xforge diff consumer. Compara projeto atual com manifest, mostra o que deveria ter sido removido mas nao foi. Exit code 0 = clean, 1 = dirty.",
                                          "phase":  "0"
                                      }
                },
    "stacks":  {
                   "detectionOrder":  [
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "*.csproj",
                                              "stack":  "dotnet"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "package.json",
                                              "stack":  "node"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "requirements.txt",
                                              "stack":  "python"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "pyproject.toml",
                                              "stack":  "python"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "go.mod",
                                              "stack":  "go"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "Cargo.toml",
                                              "stack":  "rust"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "angular.json",
                                              "stack":  "angular"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "next.config.js",
                                              "stack":  "next"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "next.config.ts",
                                              "stack":  "next"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "pom.xml",
                                              "stack":  "java"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "build.gradle",
                                              "stack":  "java"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "Gemfile",
                                              "stack":  "ruby"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "composer.json",
                                              "stack":  "php"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "mix.exs",
                                              "stack":  "elixir"
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "signal":  "*.html",
                                              "stack":  "html"
                                          }
                                      ],
                   "skipDirectories":  [
                                           "node_modules",
                                           "bin",
                                           "obj",
                                           "dist",
                                           "build",
                                           ".next",
                                           ".venv",
                                           "venv",
                                           "__pycache__",
                                           ".git"
                                       ]
               },
